1
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,720
Please enjoy.

2
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:05,970
Inspectors.

3
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:08,120
Mr. Zhou,

4
00:01:08,320 --> 00:01:09,440
we're here today because

5
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,680
we have some questions for you.

6
00:01:12,560 --> 00:01:14,200
That gilded Guan Yu statue

7
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,520
you commissioned,

8
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:16,640
where was it made?

9
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:19,320
After it was finished, was it sent to your home first

10
00:01:19,320 --> 00:01:21,120
before being sent to Dehua Bank?

11
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,680
I had this Guan Yu statue

12
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,340
made in the French Concession

13
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,880
at Baogong Workshop.

14
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:29,240
Their process

15
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,880
is famously rigorous.

16
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,560
From start to finish,

17
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,130
I went to check on it five times.

18
00:01:35,320 --> 00:01:36,039
Yesterday,

19
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,240
I saw with my own eyes

20
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,300
that old craftsman

21
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,370
put the statue into the glass case.

22
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:43,120
Because the bank

23
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:46,200
and Baogong Workshop are both in the French Concession,

24
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,320
so I had the workshop arrange for a porter

25
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,600
to carry the statue

26
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:51,130
directly to the bank today.

27
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:53,479
We will investigate Baogong Workshop.

28
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,200
But since the deceased's body

29
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,840
replaced your gift,

30
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,520
we are worried the killer

31
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,850
might be targeting you.

32
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:03,480
We'd like to inspect your home

33
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:05,040
to see if there's anything unusual.

34
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,570
Is that convenient for you?

35
00:02:07,960 --> 00:02:08,639
Of course.

36
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,820
This room was cleaned quite thoroughly.

37
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,810
It looks like bloodstains.

38
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:19,600
I'll go see if I can help.

39
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,200
Please wait.

40
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,480
We have some questions

41
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,010
and need your cooperation.

42
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:33,560
Where is your wife?

43
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,880
No. What does this

44
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,520
have to do with my wife?

45
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,240
Mr. Zhou.

46
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:40,200
Last night,

47
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,240
between 10:30 and 11:30,

48
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,140
where were you?

49
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:44,160
Wait, Inspector Lin.

50
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:44,960
What do you mean?

51
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,240
Are you suspecting me?

52
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,920
Don't misunderstand.

53
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:48,920
It's just routine procedure.

54
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,980
Please cooperate.

55
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,120
Last night,

56
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,240
I was auditing accounts at Fenghui Bank

57
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,200
until 9:00 p.m.

58
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,360
I was a bit hungry,

59
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,680
so I went to a noodle shop in the Concession.

60
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,880
I had a bowl of noodles

61
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,840
and a drink.

62
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,180
Which noodle shop?

63
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:07,960
Kangren Noodle Shop.

64
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:12,490
Around what time did you leave?

65
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,370
And where did you go after that?

66
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,940
I stayed for quite a while.

67
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:19,200
I stayed until about midnight

68
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:20,240
before I left.

69
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:22,320
I went straight home after leaving.

70
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,160
Exactly the same.

71
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,580
It seems Comprador Zhou lied.

72
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:35,300
Not only did the deceased visit his home,

73
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:36,960
but it's also very likely

74
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,220
that his home is the primary crime scene.

75
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:41,440
The most important thing for us now

76
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:42,440
is to figure out

77
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,360
exactly who

78
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:46,170
would go to such great lengths to expose the body.

79
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:09,760
Sorry.

80
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,080
We're not open yet today.

81
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,610
Why don't you wait a moment?

82
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,240
We came here today

83
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:15,880
to ask you some questions.

84
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,400
We're from the Central Police Station.

85
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:18,560
Do you want to order Lo mein?

86
00:05:18,560 --> 00:05:19,490
I can deliver it.

87
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:20,840
Shisan.

88
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,200
Why are you dawdling?

89
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:27,440
Ladies.

90
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,440
I'm sorry.

91
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,600
We have limited ingredients.

92
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,640
Everything for today is reserved.

93
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,520
Please come back another day.

94
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,240
Boss.

95
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,080
We are not here for noodles today.

96
00:05:39,080 --> 00:05:40,440
We're mainly here to see you

97
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,700
to ask a few questions.

98
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,880
Detectives.

99
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:46,460
Let's talk inside.

100
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:51,880
Mr. Zhang,

101
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,920
what time does our shop close every day?

102
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,760
As soon as the noodles are sold out,

103
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,720
we close.

104
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,360
There is no

105
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,840
fixed time.

106
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:02,920
Uncle,

107
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,650
you're here.

108
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:05,960
Here I am, Shisan.

109
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,000
They were caught fresh

110
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,130
early this morning.

111
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,000
Comprador Zhou Shiqing.

112
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:14,960
Do you know him?

113
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,120
Yes, I do.

114
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,520
He is a regular here.

115
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,720
He loves our signature dish,

116
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,240
Crab Roe Noodles.

117
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,960
Did Comprador Zhou come here

118
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,240
the night before last?

119
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,040
Yes, he did.

120
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:29,840
At that time,

121
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,200
he sat right by the entrance,

122
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,600
at the table on the right.

123
00:06:34,159 --> 00:06:35,680
He ordered a bowl of noodles,

124
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,680
and I think he had some wine.

125
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,120
Do you remember what time

126
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,320
he arrived that day?

127
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,080
It must have been

128
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:46,760
around 9:30 p.m.

129
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,080
We have a routine here.

130
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,240
Every night at nine,

131
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:53,300
we prepare the stock for the next day.

132
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:54,400
At that time,

133
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:57,320
I had just put the ingredients in the pot

134
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:58,330
when he arrived.

135
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,160
Do you remember

136
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,920
when he left?

137
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,680
As for when he left,

138
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,680
I really can't recall.

139
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,090
Detectives,

140
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,760
I just remembered something.

141
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:18,370
I don't know if it helps.

142
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,640
Go ahead.

143
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,920
The night before last,

144
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,360
I was busy in the front yard.

145
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,400
I felt so tired,

146
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,120
so I wanted to go to the inner room to rest for a bit.

147
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,440
At that time, the radio

148
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,400
was playing a song called "Drizzle."

149
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:32,440
After listening, I didn't dare rest long,

150
00:07:32,440 --> 00:07:34,120
so I went back to work.

151
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,520
I noticed at that time,

152
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,520
Comprador Zhou was no longer there.

153
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,760
Thank you.

154
00:07:42,159 --> 00:07:43,090
You're welcome.

155
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,810
Bao Workshop is a time-honored brand.

156
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,520
We've never had any mishaps.

157
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:53,480
About this matter,

158
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,409
it really has nothing to do with us.

159
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,360
Before,

160
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,960
where was that Guan Gong statue?

161
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,600
Come.

162
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,720
Look at this room.

163
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,040
This room,

164
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,320
is where we usually store our finished products.

165
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:05,560
It is so strange.

166
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:08,160
The statue of Lord Guan just disappeared.

167
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:11,280
When was the last time

168
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,280
you inspected the goods that night?

169
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:14,960
Seven in the evening.

170
00:08:15,280 --> 00:08:17,320
We closed up after the inspection

171
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,600
and left a worker to watch the room.

172
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,400
At seven the night before last,

173
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,160
were you here the whole time?

174
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:27,280
Yes, I was.

175
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:28,280
I didn't move an inch?

176
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:28,960
Not an inch.

177
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,480
According to the rules of Baogong Workshop,

178
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:36,809
smoking isn't allowed in this room, is it?

179
00:08:37,520 --> 00:08:39,049
You smell heavily of smoke.

180
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,600
Did you go out for a smoke that night?

181
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:43,860
I'm asking you!

182
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,680
Let me tell you something. Whatever you say,

183
00:08:45,680 --> 00:08:47,360
if it affects our investigation,

184
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:50,040
you will be held accountable too. Do you understand?

185
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,920
I am terribly sorry.

186
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,880
I had a craving for a smoke that night,

187
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:54,120
so I went out for a little while.

188
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,800
What time did you go out?

189
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,060
How long were you gone?

190
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,640
It was around 2:00 a.m.

191
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:01,210
I was out for 20 minutes.

192
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,340
Is this back door always open?

193
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,000
It's open when moving timber.

194
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,530
Usually, it's bolted shut.

195
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,080
Smarty.

196
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,240
Smarty, come here.

197
00:09:34,640 --> 00:09:35,920
Smarty, come. Come in.

198
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:40,960
Why is the Guan Gong statue here?

199
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,220
We thought it was lost.

200
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,080
This is the one Comprador Zhou ordered.

201
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,200
Yes, this is it.

202
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,400
Take a good look.

203
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:48,200
That's right.

204
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,960
You mean,

205
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,200
this person,

206
00:09:58,200 --> 00:10:01,000
while the Baogong Workshop worker was out for a smoke,

207
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:02,930
sneaked in through the front door,

208
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,240
then opened the back door

209
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:05,700
and moved the body inside.

210
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:09,200
That Guan Gong statue is half a man's height.

211
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:11,130
Swapping the body would take time.

212
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,520
It's possible that when the worker returned,

213
00:10:13,520 --> 00:10:15,040
the person was still there,

214
00:10:15,040 --> 00:10:17,570
so he had to escape through that small window,

215
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:19,200
and tore his clothes.

216
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:21,000
I think we can go to various tailor shops

217
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,920
and ask around.

218
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:25,400
We should be able to find the source of this fabric.

219
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,280
Smarty-pants,

220
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:29,680
that name suits you more and more.

221
00:10:32,760 --> 00:10:34,160
I found the program list.

222
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:35,920
Li Minghui's "Drizzle"

223
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,120
aired at 10:00 PM the night before last.

224
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,920
The song is four minutes long.

225
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,600
Zhang Shisan said

226
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:46,620
he went to the front courtyard after the song ended,

227
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:49,280
which was around 10:04 PM.

228
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,330
By then, Comprador Zhou

229
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,520
had already left.

230
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:56,640
He stayed until about 12:00 AM,

231
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,970
and went straight home after leaving.

232
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:02,090
Then he had plenty of time to commit the crime.

233
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,960
Where is Comprador Zhou?

234
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,720
My master drove out.

235
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:09,560
Where did he go?

236
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:10,800
How would I know?

237
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,400
He went out alone.

238
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:13,930
He was in a hurry.

239
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,760
If he wants to run,

240
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,480
the nearest exit from the city

241
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:21,880
is the south gate of the French Concession.

242
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:06,320
Looks like we're a step too late.

243
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:10,080
Time of death was within the last two hours.

244
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,920
Judging by the wound,

245
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,800
it was caused by a blunt instrument.

246
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:40,640
Judging by the length, it's a woman's.

247
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:42,520
And it's permed.

248
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:49,080
The blood residue found at Comprador Zhou's home

249
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,210
matches the victim.

250
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,840
The thread found

251
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:54,280
matches the sutures on the victim's abdomen.

252
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,720
We now have reason to suspect

253
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,920
that Comprador Zhou killed the victim.

254
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,120
However, right now...

255
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,120
the murderer you suspect is dead.

256
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,160
Could the person who killed Comprador Zhou

257
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:07,160
be the one who dug up the female body

258
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:09,000
to expose him?

259
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,440
It's possible.

260
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,560
But if his goal

261
00:13:12,560 --> 00:13:14,880
was to expose Comprador Zhou's murder

262
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:16,920
and bring him to justice,

263
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,240
he was about to succeed.

264
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:21,640
Why kill Comprador Zhou beforehand?

265
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,760
We should first figure out

266
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:38,460
why Comprador Zhou was in a rush to drive to the wilderness.

267
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:41,740
We checked Comprador Zhou's car.

268
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:44,040
The engine was off and it was locked.

269
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,280
The keys were in his pocket.

270
00:13:46,560 --> 00:13:48,000
So it's very likely

271
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,930
he arranged to meet someone there.

272
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,890
And they probably knew each other.

273
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,480
If the killer

274
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,440
just wanted to kill Comprador Zhou,

275
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:59,040
there was no need to cause such a big commotion.

276
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,120
This case isn't simple.

277
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:02,640
Everyone be careful.

278
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:05,040
I have news.

279
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,840
I sent someone to check Sanhe Hotel.

280
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:09,600
The landlady said

281
00:14:09,600 --> 00:14:11,560
there really was such a female tenant.

282
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,890
Her name is He Xiaolian.

283
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:14,240
But in the archives,

284
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,960
I couldn't find any information on her.

285
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,840
So I sent my men to check

286
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,700
every girls' school in Shanghai.

287
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:22,080
But none of the schools had her.

288
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,200
That girl

289
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,280
doesn't talk much.

290
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,480
She keeps to herself.

291
00:14:34,760 --> 00:14:35,160
Also,

292
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:36,520
she basically spends the whole day

293
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,480
sleeping.

294
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,380
She only goes out at night.

295
00:14:39,480 --> 00:14:41,610
And she always dresses like a student.

296
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:43,320
So you mean

297
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,780
she's not a student at all?

298
00:14:45,040 --> 00:14:46,440
Definitely not.

299
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:48,360
Look at her. She doesn't look like a student.

300
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:49,680
She doesn't even have a pen.

301
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:50,240
Besides,

302
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,640
who has classes in the middle of the night?

303
00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:53,640
If you ask me,

304
00:14:53,640 --> 00:14:55,800
she's probably a prostitute.

305
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:57,680
Landlady.

306
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:59,320
Thanks a lot.

307
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:00,520
Here's the thing.

308
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:03,360
We can't have outsiders watching while we investigate.

309
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:06,480
Why is there a fishy smell in here?

310
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:33,000
Opium.

311
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:34,920
I know why

312
00:15:34,920 --> 00:15:37,050
the killer took the victim's stomach.

313
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,080
It changed color.

314
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,760
The victim's intestinal tissue

315
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:53,280
changed color with Froehde's reagent

316
00:15:53,280 --> 00:15:56,200
due to the alkaloids in opium.

317
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:58,360
And look at this color.

318
00:15:58,680 --> 00:16:00,200
The concentration is high.

319
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:00,680
That means

320
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:01,840
before He Xiaolian died,

321
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,880
she consumed a large amount of opium.

322
00:16:03,880 --> 00:16:06,360
If He Xiaolian had smoked the opium,

323
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:09,680
the alkaloids would be distributed in the blood,

324
00:16:09,680 --> 00:16:10,440
liver,

325
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:11,360
lungs,

326
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:12,560
and other organs.

327
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:15,300
But they wouldn't appear in the intestines.

328
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:17,440
Especially in such large quantities.

329
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,960
It must be the intestinal lining

330
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,680
being soaked in opium.

331
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:22,320
You mean

332
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,040
body packing?

333
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:27,720
The victim

334
00:16:28,160 --> 00:16:31,000
likely put opium in fish intestines,

335
00:16:31,360 --> 00:16:32,560
swallowed them,

336
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:35,120
and used a string in her mouth

337
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,880
to pull the drugs out.

338
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,960
So the cause of death

339
00:16:39,120 --> 00:16:41,400
was likely the fish intestines rupturing inside,

340
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,120
causing opium poisoning.

341
00:16:43,680 --> 00:16:45,040
After the drugs leaked,

342
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:47,440
they passed through the respiratory and digestive tracts

343
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,640
and entered the body.

344
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:51,560
The victim would suffer respiratory failure

345
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,080
and a drop in body temperature.

346
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:55,200
Finally, due to paralysis of the respiratory center,

347
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,600
she died of suffocation.

348
00:16:57,560 --> 00:16:58,640
So,

349
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:01,240
He Xiaolian was likely using this method

350
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,400
to transport drugs.

351
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:05,760
And we can't rule out the possibility of prostitution.

352
00:17:05,760 --> 00:17:08,000
When He Xiaolian went to Comprador Zhou's house that night,

353
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:10,859
could she have been conducting such a transaction?

354
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:11,960
It's very likely.

355
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:14,839
Her stomach was removed

356
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,960
to hide the fact

357
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:18,420
that she was using her body to smuggle drugs.

358
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,960
But the body was already buried.

359
00:17:21,319 --> 00:17:21,800
That means

360
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:24,160
the killer thought the body was well hidden.

361
00:17:24,160 --> 00:17:25,880
So why remove the stomach?

362
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:28,520
What if the killer removed the stomach

363
00:17:28,560 --> 00:17:29,440
just to retrieve

364
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:32,170
the remaining drugs inside the fish intestines?

365
00:17:32,320 --> 00:17:34,200
The killer is truly heartless.

366
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:39,600
The French Concession hasn't explicitly banned the opium trade.

367
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:42,320
But it is explicitly banned in the Chinese territory.

368
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:44,280
He Xiaolian definitely has more buyers

369
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,740
than just Comprador Zhou.

370
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:48,720
And if they were transporting drugs in the French Concession,

371
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:50,920
there would be no need for such trouble.

372
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:54,050
The buyers might all be in the Chinese territory.

373
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:57,040
But we don't have jurisdiction in the Chinese territory.

374
00:17:57,040 --> 00:17:58,840
And even if we found those buyers,

375
00:17:58,840 --> 00:18:00,170
they wouldn't admit it.

376
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:07,700
Have you seen He Xiaolian?

377
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,520
I have never seen this lady.

378
00:18:11,360 --> 00:18:14,020
You haven't seen Comprador Zhou bring her home?

379
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:15,560
No.

380
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:19,080
Between 10:00 and 11:30 the night before last,

381
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:20,810
did you not see Comprador Zhou?

382
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,760
I was in my own room.

383
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,170
The Master said before he left that day

384
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:27,120
that he would bring his keys.

385
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:28,920
Does Comprador Zhou have any

386
00:18:28,920 --> 00:18:30,240
close female associates?

387
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:32,100
Especially in the last day or two.

388
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,200
Last year,

389
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:35,520
the Master met a dancer

390
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:38,240
from the Grand Shanghai Dance Hall.

391
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:40,440
Her name is Haitang.

392
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,480
A few times,

393
00:18:41,840 --> 00:18:44,080
while the Madam was back in her hometown,

394
00:18:44,080 --> 00:18:45,810
the Master went to see Haitang.

395
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:47,680
I remember now.

396
00:18:48,040 --> 00:18:49,300
The night before last,

397
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:51,920
Miss Haitang came to see the Master.
